OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fshowers lingering into this evening,
OL,7,Fthese could turn heavy at times.
OL,8,FBecoming mostly dry through the early
OL,9,Fhours of the morning with some clear
OL,10,Fspells developing. Lighter winds but a
OL,11,Fcool breeze remains around coastlines.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FThe odd early shower is
OL,14,Fpossible, otherwise a dry day with
OL,15,Flight winds. Cloudy at times, but with
OL,16,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Feeling
OL,17,Fless chilly in the lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
