OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLots
OL,6,Fof dry weather on Saturday but the odd
OL,7,Fshower still possible. Showers early
OL,8,Fon Sunday but brighter by the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Turning unsettled later on
OL,10,FMonday. Average temperatures.
